narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Mnr Industries LLC is a Clinic/Center  Urgent Care provider based in Bel Air, MD. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $107.5M in Medicaid payments across 1.9M claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: This provider received $107.5M in taxpayer-funded Medicaid payments — enough to fund healthcare for approximately 13,440 Medicaid beneficiaries for a full year at average per-enrollee costs.
